body: Although I don't know Chinese I get the message of this manga. Also, it was a good fap 10/10

Sudoku is a Japanese chess game.

Seppuku is the act of cutting opens one stomach to commit suicide. Usually done with a katana during the world war II and before. It is an act which is done to preserve one's honor, for example you kill yourself so your enemy does not have the honor of killing you.

123. So the monster represents the mental illness that sprouted from the pressure of the world on young girls to meet impossible beauty standards, which led to her committing sudoku. Asphyxiation was nice though. Good fap
